"Cover"

At Quantico, Alex finally receives
information about her father and his FBI
past, but in the future it s her mother,
Sita, who plays a key role when Liam
convinces her to participate in a press
conference on national television
begging Alex to turn herself in. Also at
Quantico,  the NATS learn the art of
profiling and focus on their classmates

comradery.
